cast.overview: When single mom Callie and her two kids Trevor and Phoebe arrive in a small Oklahoma town, they begin to discover their connection to the original Ghostbusters and the secret legacy their grandfather left behind.
cast.title: Ghostbusters: Afterlife

details.biography: Sarah Natochenny is a Voice Arts Award-winning actor best known for her work in the role of Ash Ketchum and 30 other characters on Pokémon since 2006. She is also an on-camera actor and film editor, working in comedy and horror. She splits her time between LA and NYC when not on location or meeting fans at conventions.
details.name: Sarah Natochenny
